ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model

Class Valve

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.APhysicalComponent
      • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.Valve
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Floodable

    public class Valve
extends APhysicalComponent
implements Floodable
    General Valve model class. Implements the physical model of a valve. Can be used for check valves, (magnetic) way valves, pressure reducing valves. Assumptions: -2 States (idle, open) -No leakage Inputlist: 1: ValveCtrl : [-] ON/OFF position of the valve. 1 means ON, 0 means OFF. Only needed for magnetic valves 2: FluidIn : [-] Outputlist: 1: PLoss : [W] : Power loss 2: PTotal : [W] : Needed electrical power to open and hold the valve 3: FluidOut : [-] Config parameters: ElectricPower : [W] PressureLossCoefficient : [-] Area : [m2]
    Author:
    kraandre
